data.description: Welcome to this 4 bed / 2 bath single story home on nearly 2 acres of land, perfect for an investor or someone looking to build their own equity. On this huge lot there is a second structure in the back that could potentially but turned into a second unit or guest home. With homes nearby selling for $700k and $800k or more this home has a ton of potential to build equity or be an amazing investment.
